<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1587:1610'>司裘王大射則共虎侯言王大射者謂王將祀五帝於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1610:1633'>四郊昊天於圓丘及享先王選助祭者故於四郊小學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1633:1656'>之中王與諸侯及羣臣等行大射之法也虎侯者謂以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1656:1679'>虎皮飾其布侯之側其鵠亦以虎皮方制之著於侯中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1679:1702'>其侯道九十弓弓二寸以為侯中中亦身也侯身廣丈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1702:1726'>八尺三分其侯而鵠居一焉則鵠方六尺矣此王之所射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1726:1749'>之侯也與梓人張皮侯而棲鵠共為一事侯制上廣下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1749:1772'>狹蓋取象於人張臂八尺張足六尺是取象率焉樂以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1772:1798'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1798:1804'>騶虞九節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1804:1830'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
